                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <locus target="#122r #122v" facs="126 127">Fols. 122r, 122v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Translation of the Hymn for Good Friday, “Lord, Remember me in your Kingdom,” from Coptic in to Gǝ`ǝz, in a different hand. Cf. Lectionary for Passion Week, ግብረ፡ ሕማማት፡
                    </desc>
                    </item>
